ent fallback was never reached. If VoiceEngine's menubar accessory stole focus during the\r\n  recording/transcription cycle, Cmd+V went to VoiceEngine instead of the target app. Text sat on the clipboard but never arrived at the cursor.\r\n \r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1mWhat changed (Paster.swift only, 3 changes)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  1. \u001b[0m\u001b[1mSnapshot \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;12mfrontmostApplication\u001b[0m at the top of \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;12mpaste() \u001b[0m— captures the real target app before any focus-shifting ops\r\n  2. \u001b[0m\u001b[1mActivate the target app \u001b[0mbefore sending Cmd+V — \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;12mapp.activate() \u001b[0mrecovers focus if VoiceEngine stole it; a cheap no-op otherwise\r\n  3. \u001b[0m\u001b[1mBumped clipboard-commit sleep\u001b[0m from 20ms → 50ms to reduce the NSPasteboard race window\r\n \r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1mVerification\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  - \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;12mswift build \u001b[0m— clean, no warnings from Paster.swift\r\n  - \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;12mswift test \u001b[0m— passes\r\n  \r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;7m✻ Baked for 4m 49s\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;7m※\u001b[0m \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;7mrecap: \u001b[0m\u001b[3m\u001b[38;5;7mVoice paste fix is done and shipped. PR #9 is open at `jwalin-shah/voice-engine-swift`, waiting for your merge. (disable recaps in /config)\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;7m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n❯ \r\n\u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;7m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;7mdeepseek/deepseek-v4-pro[1m] | ctx: 10% used\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;9m⏵⏵ byp